        <mxCell id="o05vOpjIfVoNKR81GA2A-6" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="When a job is accepted, it will note landmarks. Something like &quot;Help, I got shot over by the Fudge shack. I tried to run away towards Corey Booker&#39;s Adult Emporeum&quot;" vertex="1">
