        <mxCell id="o05vOpjIfVoNKR81GA2A-7" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="After following the navigation the ambulance will arrive in the general area. The story lot (The Fudge Shack) will have spawned several other lots, some being the clue lot (Corey&#39;s XXX) and the victim will be in a small radius between them&amp;nbsp;" vertex="1">
